Name: Duloga
About the game: Duloga is a reverse space shooter where you choose who lives and dies. Can You Survive 7 Nights? FEATURING... Seven full levels. Can you SURVIVE all of them? State-of-the-art RGB COLORS! GUIDE a crowd to weed out criminals! High resolution 8-BIT GRAPHICS! Help COPS meet their quota! CHOOSE who deserves to die. Duloga is a game about our struggle against police brutality, extrajudicial killings, red-tagging, and state terrorism in the Philippines.
